text: Manali Kishor Dakshini (born 29 September 1997) is a Maharashtrian cricketer. She is a right arm medium pacer and right hand bat. She plays for Mumbai and West Zone. She has played 3 First-class matches, 11 Limited over matches and 21 Women's Twenty20. In January 2019, she was named in India Blue's team for the 2018–19 Senior Women's Challenger Trophy. She was one of the top performers of challengers trophy held in jan 2019 with remarkable all round performance. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Mumbai women cricketers Category:West Zone women cricketers Category:People from Thane
